---
// Statistics.astro - Statistics section showcasing FiNAN's impact
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4 font-medium">
        Our Impact in Numbers
      </p>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight"
          >
            Empowering Filipino<br />Nurses Across the Nordics
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            From building a strong professional community to guiding nurses
            through licensing and integration, FiNAN's work is reflected in the
            numbers. These stats highlight our reach, impact, and dedication to
            our members.
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a
              href="https://filnan.com/membership-form"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-gray-900 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors text-center"
            >
              Become a Member
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://filnan.com/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-gray-900 font-medium hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors text-center"
            >
              About FiNAN
              <svg
                class="ml-2 w-4 h-4"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Statistics Cards -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Registered Members -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
        <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          500+
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">
          Registered Members
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Across 5 Nordic countries, united under FiNAN's mission.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Success Rate -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
        <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">99%</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">
          Licensing Success Rate
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Members who obtained Nordic RN licenses with FiNAN's guidance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Funds Raised -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
        <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          €15K
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Funds Raised</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          For humanitarian projects and community support.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
